fields.title: TIUM RESTAURANT MANAGEMENT SYSTEM
fields.description:
Scope & Requirements (Summary)
Core Modules: POS, table/floor management, menu/recipe management, inventory & supplier management, staff roles & permissions, cash/shift management, tax & pricing rules, discounts/comps, voids, and audit logs.


Reports & Analytics: Daily sales, category/item performance, inventory usage & variance, staff performance, cash reconciliation, and custom reports as specified.


Integrations (if any): [Payment provider], [Accounting], [SMS/Email], [Kitchen Display System], [Delivery aggregator], etc.


Environment: [Cloud/on-prem], browser/mobile endpoints, user limits, and backups.


Non-Functional: Security, role-based access, uptime target, backup/restore, and performance expectations.
